markets.description:
Kamala Harris is scheduled to give an interview on CNN on August 29, 2024. This market refers to anything Harris says during the interview. 

This market will resolve to "Yes" if Harris says "DEI" or "Diversity, Equity, and Inclusion" during the interview. Otherwise, the market will resolve to "No".

Any usage of the word regardless of context will count toward the resolution of this market.

Pluralization/possessive of the word will count toward the resolution of this market, however other forms will NOT count.

Compound words will count as long as "DEI" is part of the compound word and references the meaning which refers to diversity, equity, and inclusion.

This market will resolve when the interview finishes airing in its entirety. If the interview has not aired in its entirety by September 9, 11:59 PM ET, this market will resolve based on what has aired up to that point.

The resolution source is the video of the interview.
